1. Fully featured, DNS Server written in Go
2. Advanced logging, query loggings
3. DDOS mitigations detection and response techniques
4. Fine tuning of DNS Server,down to protocol features, advanced features, and experimental DNS
5. Full support for integration with the dnsscience.io platform for threat intelligence feeds and anonymous analytics submission, all configurable
6. Data sharing levels with dnsscience.io configurable.
7. Support plugins
8. Init scripts, daemon,cli tools, dns debugging tools
9. dnsscience client written in go, study ~/development/dnsscience.io/
10. check out ~/development/adsdnsgo/
11. lets write it in go
12. modules support, so we can make plugins


